{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/spooktacularkit\/provisioning"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/Provisioning"},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"macOS virtual machines don’t have a cloud-init equivalent. Spooktacular"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provides provisioning modes to bridge this gap. Today, SSH provisioning"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is fully working. Disk-inject is in progress, and two more modes (guest"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"agent and shared-folder watcher) are planned."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Choosing-a-Mode","text":"Choosing a Mode","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Mode"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Status"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Works without setup?"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Network needed?"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Best for"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/ssh","type":"reference","isActive":true}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Working","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Need SSH enabled","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Yes","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Cloned VMs with SSH","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/diskInject"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In progress","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Yes"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Fresh IPSW installs, CI runners"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/agent"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Planned"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Need agent installed"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OCI images (future)"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/sharedFolder"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Planned"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Need watcher"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No-disk-modify environments"}]}]]],"header":"row","type":"table"},{"anchor":"SSH-Working","text":"SSH (Working)","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"After boot, Spooktacular discovers the VM’s IP, connects via SSH,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and executes your script. You get real-time output streaming."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"bash","code":["spook start my-vm \\","    --user-data ~\/setup.sh \\","    --provision ssh \\","    --ssh-user admin"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Requires:"}]},{"type":"text","text":" Remote Login enabled in the guest"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(System Settings -> General -> Sharing -> Remote Login)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Disk-Inject-In-Progress","text":"Disk Inject (In Progress)","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Before the VM boots, Spooktacular mounts the guest’s data volume"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and writes a standard macOS LaunchDaemon that executes your script."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is the only mode that will work on a completely vanilla macOS"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"install. This mode is currently being implemented."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"bash","code":["spook create my-vm --from-ipsw latest \\","    --user-data ~\/setup.sh \\","    --provision disk-inject"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Guest-Agent-Planned","text":"Guest Agent (Planned)","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The Spooktacular guest agent will communicate over VirtIO socket — a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"direct host-guest channel that works without networking. This mode"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is planned for a future release."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Shared-Folder-Planned","text":"Shared Folder (Planned)","level":3,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The script will be delivered via a VirtIO shared folder. A watcher"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"daemon in the guest will execute new scripts automatically. This"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"mode is planned for a future release."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"API Collection","modules":[{"name":"SpooktacularKit"}],"role":"collectionGroup","title":"Provisioning Virtual Machines"},"abstract":[{"text":"Run scripts aut